Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:01:01.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:04.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:07.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:14.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:21.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.51,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:28.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:35.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:40.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:47.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:57.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:21.36,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち止まらず歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:24.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星を数えるより
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:29.80,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消せない絆が光るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:37.24,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夢は走りだした僕らを導いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:41.61,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願いを込めて描く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:46.83,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}守りたい気持ちはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:52.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち向かう勇気くれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.45,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まっすぐ伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:58.48,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:01.68,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けて　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:05.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\}忘れない胸の奥で輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.32,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がくれた光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:11.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一緒に　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.30,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:18.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強く握りしめる手は暖かく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:23.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと離さないよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:21.36,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:24.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不必计数天上星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:29.80,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:37.24,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:41.61,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:46.83,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:52.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.45,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:58.48,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:01.68,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:05.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.32,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:11.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.30,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:18.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:23.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
